## 1. Purpose

This Requirements Traceability Matrix provides forward and backward traceability for all requirements in `docs/SRS.md`. Every requirement traces from source (SRS) through design (SDD) through implementation (code files) to verification (UAT test case) and closure (PR SHA).

**Forward traceability**: REQ → SDD → Code → UAT

**Backward traceability**: UAT → Code → SDD → REQ

This document is the authoritative source for CMMI audit evidence. Keep it updated with every PR that touches a requirement.

