## 7. Audit Note

Per CMMI v3.0 RDM SP 1.4 (Maintain Bidirectional Traceability of Requirements): this document is evidence of bidirectional traceability. SCAMPI assessors should find every SRS requirement represented in this table with at least one implementation file and one test reference before status "Closed" is claimed.

Gaps in "Source files" or "UAT test ID" columns indicate open traceability items that must be resolved before the RTM row reaches "Verified".
